        <mxCell id="8" value="Build API Messages:&#xa;• system: &#39;You are an expert in industrial waste heat.&#xa;  Output ONLY one of: Water, Exhaust, Steam, Air, Oil, Refrigerant&#39;&#xa;• user: col1 + col2 text" style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fillColor=#fff2cc;strokeColor=#d6b656;fontSize=11;align=left;" parent="1" vertex="1">
